{"tid":1647593,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有認真思考過最近嘅自殺事件","createTime":"2019-10-11T22:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T16:29:41.000Z","uid":79326,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6e847918f0bedc140a01a11d9f1afb67b74cf696","tid":1647593,"uid":79326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T22:20:48.000Z","msg":"黑警打死人，係呢個香港社會已經好似係平常事咁。。<br />\n新屋嶺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我更加擔心既係，<br />\n香港除咗警察同埋示威者，其實仲有好多唔同人，有冇諗過以前啲黑社會？殺手去晒邊？<br />\n<br />\n假如我係壞人，我知道而家無論做啲咩都會入黑警數，我老閪都去做啦！要殺人嘅殺人要打劫既打劫。<br />\n<br />\n唔係想帶風向話唔關黑警事，我絕對相信手足講嘅野！<br />\n<br />\n而係喺呢個社會當警察已經冇用嘅時候我哋更加要去保護市民！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔可以俾啲壞人覺得社會亂佢就可以為所欲為，因為有太多自殺案都好鬼，我哋唔可以自動排除左係有人謀殺！<br />\n<br />\n希望無論連登定係其他文宣要宣揚信息要保護市民呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022330c5d61b1b8eea6f9c31278a4777ed944e4c","tid":1647593,"uid":79326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T22:21:12.000Z","msg":"五大訴求！"},{"pid":"076d6b63e3a6f1645a65524148c535bee78d8acc","tid":1647593,"uid":79326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T22:21:24.000Z","msg":"缺一不可！"},{"pid":"9c79380206194bcf2c8acce666ba09062b0c32fd","tid":1647593,"uid":79326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T22:21:51.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"e097b9307ef8d5a50be3ec2330e6c496f00414ca","tid":1647593,"uid":217103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T22:22:57.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"35e85303ef405724225abdbb5a4d401675461258","tid":1647593,"uid":79326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T22:34:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1a235d93bca31a4b58879a5b7e1af62578ace46f","tid":1647593,"uid":300690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score